{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glslify-bundle\">glslify-bundle</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"></a></p>\n<p>Bundle a <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glslify-deps\">glslify-deps</a> dependency tree into\na GLSL source string.</p>\n<p>This has been separated from <em>glslify-deps</em> such that you can prebundle a dependency\ntree server-side, but then still modify shader file contents in a browser.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/glslify-bundle/\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"-source-bundle-deps-\"><code>source = bundle(deps)</code></h3>\n<p>Takes the output object from <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glslify-deps\">glslify-deps</a>\nand returns a bundled GLSL string.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;bundle&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"support function js\"><span>require</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&apos;</span></span><span>glslify-bundle</span><span class=\"punctuation definition string end js\"><span>&apos;</span></span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>)</span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span class=\"storage type var js\"><span>var</span></span><span>&#xA0;deps&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"keyword operator assignment js\"><span>=</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"support function js\"><span>require</span></span><span class=\"meta brace round js\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"string quoted single js\"><span class=\"punctuation definition string begin js\"><span>&apos;</span></span><span>gl